             = The Legend of Korra (comics series)\n|charsort            = <!-- If \"character\" is set -->\n|addpubcat#          = \n}}\n'''''The Legend of Korra''''' comics are a continuation of the [[Nickelodeon]] [[Animated cartoon|animated television series]] of ''[[The Legend of Korra]]'', created by [[Michael Dante DiMartino]] and [[Bryan Konietzko]]. Chronologically, the comics take place after the series finale, \"The Last Stand\". They are published by [[Dark Horse Comics]], the same company that publishes the [[Avatar: The Last Airbender (comics)|''Avatar: The Last Airbender'' comics]].\n\n==Short stories==\n\nShort ''The Legend of Korra'' comics have appeared in Dark Horse's [[Free Comic Book Day]] 2016 and 2018 issues.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n!Title\n!Date\n!Story\n!Art\n!Colors\n!FCBD issue\n|-\n|'''\"Friends for Life\"'''\n|May 7, 2016\n|[[Michael Dante DiMartino]]\n|Heather Campbell\n|Killian Ng\n|''The Legend of Korra / How to Train Your Dragon / Plants vs. Zombies''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://digital.darkhorse.com/books/3f39e6a81d2b42c68cdbab067b7825a5/free-comic-book-day-2016-korra-all-ages|title=FCBD 2016: The Legend of Korra / How to Train Your Dragon / Plants vs. Zombies|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=January 26, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|'''\"Lost Pets\"'''\n|May 5, 2018\n|[[Michael Dante DiMartino]]\n|Jayd A\u00eft-Kaci\n|Killian Ng\n|''The Legend of Korra & Nintendo ARMS''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.freecomicbookday.com/Catalog/JAN180023|title=FCBD 2018 LEGEND OF KORRA & NINTENDO ARMS|work=freecomicbookday.com|accessdate=January 13, 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Graphic novel trilogies==\nA continuation of ''The Legend of Korra'' television series in comics form, published by [[Dark Horse Comics]]. It immediately takes place where the animated show left off.\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n!Title\n!Date\n!Story\n!Script\n!Art\n!Colors\n!Cover\n!Notes\n|-\n|rowspan=3|'''''[[The Legend of Korr